				 Broken Arm = Less Brent for a While 

				 
					 May 10, 2014 Brent Blog Posts 4  Comments 				 
			 
		 

			 
 I tripped while carrying a monitor, and before you could say “banana peel” the top of my  humerus bone  was smashed: 
 As they say on Mythbusters, “There’s your problem.” 
 The surgeons think it broke completely across, but they don’t want to pop me open to do 